於1946年4月開始運轉，位於荷蘭海牙。國際法院的主要功能是對各國所提交的案件做出有法律約束力的仲裁，並就正式認可的聯合國機關和專門機構提交的法律問題提供諮詢意見。國際法院是具有明確權限的民事法院，沒有附屬機構，對其他國際法庭沒有管轄權。國際法院沒有刑事管轄權，因此無法審判個人，這種刑事審判由國內管轄或聯合國特設刑事法庭或國際刑事法院管轄。"},{"pid":"092adbb2bb07c4527c476d46a8ebb39b0b637f6b","tid":1536372,"uid":252960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49ce30bcc46ec2b842d506b872f3b104f5ef4f2b","tid":1536372,"uid":154808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0793bbccf53f9fff45143fb3cb781ef0d1044046","tid":1536372,"uid":252960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:22:01.000Z","msg":"屌我一早提過啦又冇人理，立場教埋點做：<br />\n<br />\n眾籌協助受害人控告濫暴警和警務處處長 呢個幾時做，冇人提？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1490880\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1490880</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:25:17.000Z","msg":"我想問既係可唔可以告執法機關"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:30:25.000Z","msg":"可以，睇入面條link：<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%87%89%E7%99%BC%E5%8B%95%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C-%E5%8D%94%E5%8A%A9%E5%8F%97%E5%AE%B3%E4%BA%BA%E6%8E%A7%E5%91%8A%E6%BF%AB%E6%9A%B4%E8%AD%A6%E5%92%8C%E8%AD%A6%E5%8B%99%E8%99%95%E8%99%95%E9%95%B7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2587%2589%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C-%25E5%258D%2594%25E5%258A%25A9%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%25AE%25B3%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%258E%25A7%25E5%2591%258A%25E6%25BF%25AB%25E6%259A%25B4%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2592%258C%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%258B%2599%25E8%2599%2595%25E8%2599%2595%25E9%2595%25B7%2F&d=KYuNOZm%2F4ip93LesI4%2B6vhVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=729d0631\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2587%2589%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C-%25E5%258D%2594%25E5%258A%25A9%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%25AE%25B3%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%258E%25A7%25E5%2591%258A%25E6%25BF%25AB%25E6%259A%25B4%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2592%258C%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%258B%2599%25E8%2599%2595%